# GitHub sync (live at all times)

- **Remote:** `origin` → https://github.com/azknoquestions/Zenith
- **Branch:** `main`

When making or suggesting changes:
- Prefer committing and pushing so GitHub stays up to date and collaborators see changes.
- Remind the user to run `git pull` when opening the project if others might have pushed.
- After significant edits, suggest: `git add . && git commit -m "description" && git push`

This repo is meant to be accessible by Cursor and stay live for collaboration.
